/** The date for which the filtering was performed. */
    private final LocalDate localDate;

The code below made me look the above field and JavaDoc. From the name and JavaDoc I can not understand what this is. The name is just the name of the type. Is this the time used to calculate all the board/alight times? In that case this is the serviceDate.

